room_title: Escape room "Deepsky" by EsQape It in Albuquerque
room_description: At the height of the cold war, 1963, Agent Deepsky of Her Majesty's Secret Service has some information to give to you. Meet her at her New York City apartment, but beware of her nemesis, Viktor Glazkov!  If he finds out that you are in contact with Agent Deepsky, he will do everything in his power to kill her... and you.
